==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sordes
<hw>Sor"des</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., fr.
<ets>sordere</ets> to be dirty or foul.]</ety> <def>Foul matter;
excretion; dregs; filthy, useless, or rejected matter of any kind;
specifically <fld>(Med.)</fld>, the foul matter that collects on the
teeth and tongue in low fevers and other conditions attended with great
vital depression.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

